{"tid":1715653,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"Logon拒罷工 禁止員工之間討論政治 齊抵制！","createTime":"2019-11-13T06:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T04:01:32.000Z","uid":280770,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5993d7ebfa6f7cac753edb6713e137b23a3d0d49","tid":1715653,"uid":280770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:49:45.000Z","msg":"代post: 事源Logon真係好鍾意返工，三罷冇一次肯參與，都算，仲要堅決要求同事返工。11月11日三罷，一樣照開門營業，出面打緊仗之際，Logon處於平衡時空，有同事討論政治話題(黑警開槍打手無寸鐵後生仔)時懷疑惹起Logon某女經理嘅不滿，要求員工之間唔可以討論政治話題。唔比討論係唔係制造緊白色恐怖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同日遲遲唔肯比員工先走，同一商場內其他商店已經一早叫自己員工先行離去，唯獨Logon，咁大間公司，但完全無視員工安全，要求員工留守，完全唔肯做少一日生意。<br />\n仲有唔比員工早走已經唔係第一次發生，據了解早前某同事遲走係街食晒催淚彈，仲話一日催淚彈唔放到黎都唔比走，究竟呢間公司對員工人生安全既定義係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日11月13日，事情發展到第三日，可能有見香港現今情況嚴峻，才決定讓同事擁有罷工機會，真係多撚謝。<br />\n<br />\n其實Logon你咁中意返工，點解唔叫埋啲高層落黎和你返。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed21f644120fcd8267e1825c52cd87daef9b63d","tid":1715653,"uid":12499,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:56:53.000Z","msg":"呢個可能要搞清楚 好多公司都冇公開講罷工<br />\n可能係個經理問題<br />\n印象佢非中資"},{"pid":"8d240f586d46d2d2f99ad78348d1119add9a8d1c","tid":1715653,"uid":51649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:22:57.000Z","msg":"代朋友覆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nlogon永遠走都係有遲無早，d人走晒，logon員工都未走得，聽佢講d經理好廢好似話唔到事咁，話要等上頭安排呢樣個樣，有朋友返名店坊logon同海港城logon ，有次放tg放到sogo門口，d防暴封晒路係維園個邊都唔比走，話商場未關門，最後我朋友要行路返屋企，想問下你邊間logon咁賤唔比人講政治，唔通個女經理係藍絲？"},{"pid":"140b56e88e376ceb6a12de6aa818fee23b48bccc","tid":1715653,"uid":291750,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JazORdx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJazORdx.jpg&h=5d43122d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c6322f8774bc43e18e6f48602be7657977f2821","tid":1715653,"uid":44061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:17:56.000Z","msg":"logon同citysuper好似同一個老細"},{"pid":"8ecf8ee11a62120e2e69d9860ad47ef257389bfb","tid":1715653,"uid":96210,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5c6322f8774bc43e18e6f48602be7657977f2821","tid":1715653,"uid":44061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:17:56.000Z","msg":"logon同citysuper好似同一個老細"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T11:30:19.000Z","msg":"係呀，班友藍到黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食開人血饅頭"},{"pid":"89176e4bf10fe2f443f9ec680d720862cd796fa9","tid":1715653,"uid":253231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:38:53.000Z","msg":"兩間根本同1集團 高層1樣藍到腦殘 何必分那麼細<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"002288cfd094d01b5fb03f73ca0ce8d2a3d32fd9","tid":1715653,"uid":40779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:44:06.000Z","msg":"日資係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fab48e80f1b445af24fbcfd7c7c5085e661207b","tid":1715653,"uid":54126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:44:18.000Z","msg":"罷買"},{"pid":"7cfecddefde8fbdf36d1584baa6f9588476062cb","tid":1715653,"uid":334806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:45:16.000Z","msg":"d嘢咁貴 罷買"},{"pid":"fe9878386a4ad28315f81a234d38aa99bb7cbcac","tid":1715653,"uid":113922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:45:59.000Z","msg":"一係炒經理一係裝修"},{"pid":"093354a4807d13fc10ec0ee8cc3784b731db8de5","tid":1715653,"uid":16185,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"002288cfd094d01b5fb03f73ca0ce8d2a3d32fd9","tid":1715653,"uid":40779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:44:06.000Z","msg":"日資係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:47:37.000Z","msg":"邊係日資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hk