ime":"2019-11-13T12:50:09.000Z","msg":"c記已經成日自己裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f39ca87c5b89349df51d32abbd9605d57fe54b2","tid":1715653,"uid":161162,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:52:58.000Z","msg":"Logon 對員工政治取態好自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：Logon 員工(part time 職員証全白 影黎無用)"},{"pid":"dd1850b01000d06f3afb629f72a0320ce870cfca","tid":1715653,"uid":96210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f39ca87c5b89349df51d32abbd9605d57fe54b2","tid":1715653,"uid":161162,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:52:58.000Z","msg":"Logon 對員工政治取態好自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：Logon 員工(part time 職員証全白 影黎無用)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:19:42.000Z","msg":"咁有遲冇早，唔到冇車都唔肯放人走，Keep住食人血饅頭，Ching有咩睇法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7480721cbb7668a7efd9cc3bc2f9107effcf33f8","tid":1715653,"uid":280770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f39ca87c5b89349df51d32abbd9605d57fe54b2","tid":1715653,"uid":161162,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:52:58.000Z","msg":"Logon 對員工政治取態好自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：Logon 員工(part time 職員証全白 影黎無用)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:26:38.000Z","msg":"講政治話題都比女經理投訴有幾自由呀？<br />\n利申：朋友都係返logon架！！"},{"pid":"bc5155a1b4c7326d0f9d87178200ef2e7ce92fff","tid":1715653,"uid":161162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd1850b01000d06f3afb629f72a0320ce870cfca","tid":1715653,"uid":96210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f39ca87c5b89349df51d32abbd9605d57fe54b2","tid":1715653,"uid":161162,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:52:58.000Z","msg":"Logon 對員工政治取態好自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：Logon 員工(part time 職員証全白 影黎無用)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:19:42.000Z","msg":"咁有遲冇早，唔到冇車都唔肯放人走，Keep住食人血饅頭，Ching有咩睇法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:43:39.000Z","msg":"Ching 依排都係黨鐵收皮前一個鐘收鋪加比人走"},{"pid":"053801029b2d8caeb88151edf5329f415bbbef6c","tid":1715653,"uid":96210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc5155a1b4c7326d0f9d87178200ef2e7ce92fff","tid":1715653,"uid":161162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd1850b01000d06f3afb629f72a0320ce870cfca","tid":1715653,"uid":96210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f39ca87c5b89349df51d32abbd9605d57fe54b2","tid":1715653,"uid":161162,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:52:58.000Z","msg":"Logon 對員工政治取態好自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：Logon 員工(part time 職員証全白 影黎無用)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:19:42.000Z","msg":"咁有遲冇早，唔到冇車都唔肯放人走，Keep住食人血饅頭，Ching有咩睇法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:43:39.000Z","msg":"Ching 依排都係黨鐵收皮前一個鐘收鋪加比人走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:52:48.000Z","msg":"Ching係講緊冇咩大事件發生嘅時候？我想知係有大事發生嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我問得唔好請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：我都有朋友做Logon FullTime，成日呻"},{"pid":"5c9d50ff6676a7068c0790e76fa434fc06ebdf85","tid":1715653,"uid":22709,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:51:21.000Z","msg":"代po<br />\n<br />\n我唔介意話埋我喺革命舖做嘅！<br />\n一：基本上都係黨鐵閂前1-1.5hrs先走，但每次都有Senior AM同AM follow，at least出面有推進/放臭蛋會即時叫名店坊間舖閃先，再後啲到我地。<br />\n<br />\n二：出面有活動（例如第一次三罷），我地舖通常都開，但唔返/返唔到嘅同事講到明唔會揪後！包括今日超市嗰邊都係得好少人返到；有買物資俾前線，雖然唔多因為窮；有幾次收1600/1700，我地成班會一齊出去（超市嗰邊都有）。<br />\n<br />\n三：有邊間大公司唔係食水深？但我仲喺度做係因為哩度有言論自由。我地唔會同客講政治，但喺廠/飯堂講冇問題；喺張枱度一齊摺白花俾第一個犧牲手足再一齊上街；同事嘅locker任貼文宣，我地有四個1.8mx1.2m嘅大鐵櫃再貼大量文宣都得，有好多叔叔嬸嬸真係有睇（有時有人偷嘢要報警仲可以俾班popo睇返自己嘅仆街嘢🖕🏼)；樓上HR同L&amp;D都批准office/前線同事喺自己位可以文宣；official fb page有次出咗條片係用memo砌咗個大pepe出嚟，班膠層咁撚怕事都可以出街；仲未計仲有校巴同大量文宣組<br />\n<br />\nSor for 1999,但我只係想講，麻煩唔好將臭hi伍小姐啲19連鎖同我地比。我地前線未試過屌手足，大量同路人，有物資出物資有力就企前啲。罷買對我影響微到爆，但對班parttime 會好大，或者有Ching有好路數就share俾佢地。最後有人要裝修嘅我冇嘢講，但會hurt因為有人將我地同藍店放埋一齊比<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NctHdEw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNctHdEw.jpg&h=cdfe98d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54e3a23fbab894ac36bf15da37a6bbb76066d3de","tid":1715653,"uid":191052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:53:01.000Z","msg":"Log on? 不了"},{"pid":"21e80cd29f86f0f03083a0ef9aaae01bb91dd24d","tid":1715653,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aed21f644120fcd8267e1825c52cd87daef9b63d","tid":1715653,"uid":12499,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:56:53.000Z","msg":"呢個可能要搞清楚 好多公司都冇公開講罷工<br />\n可能係個經理問題<br />\n印象佢非中資"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:32:56.000Z","msg":"c!ty'super"}]}